## Source: ossf-package-analysis (aa4de351aa4b33df056e33ba724412cd5826482a919ebadd8bd3452e04d990e4)
The OpenSSF Package Analysis project identified 'enjin-docs' @ 8.0.0 (npm) as malicious.

- The package executes one or more commands associated with malicious behavior.
